Metadata: Washington Coast Shellfish Aquaculture Study: Working Group Process

Ongoing activities for this aquaculture study include: Quantitative comparisons of intertidal processes; Ongoing research assists working group and Working group communications between workshops. This one pager lists when all four workshops will be held: Workshop 1: October 28-29, 2019; Workshp 2: Spring 2020; Workshop 3: Fall 2020; and Workshop 4: Spring 2021.
